Name: Quantifying Loop Gain using Dynamical Modelling of Ventilatory Control - Data and Code
Version: 2.0
Description: This dataset and code support an automated method to quantify Loop Gain (LG) from RIP signals to assist with personalized sleep apnea treatment. The model achieves accurate LG estimation across apnea phenotypes using data from 465 patients.
Documentation: https://bdsp.io/content/hlg-data-code/2.0/
Contact: Not explicitly listed; authors include Thijs Nassi, Yalda Amidi, M. B. Westover, Robert Thomas
ManagedBy: "[Massachusetts General Hospital & Brain Data Science Platform](https://bdsp.io)"
UpdateFrequency: Static – versioned dataset (v2.0)
Tags:
